@productId2 = cf7e3b8a-a7b7-4c8c-84c5-d682d2b549d3

### Create order
POST {{baseUrl}}/order/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "owner": "{{ownerId}}",
  "location": "{{locationId}}",
  "productIds": [
    "{{productId1}}",
    "{{productId2}}"
  ]
}

> {% if (response.status === 201) { client.global.set("orderId", response.body.orderId); } %}

### Get order by id
GET {{baseUrl}}/order/663e7e2b-ba24-4e32-bdf6-7119f5bd08f2

> {% if (response.status === 200 && response.body.positions?.length) { client.global.set("orderItemId", response.body.positions[0].id); } %}

### Update order status
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/order/663e7e2b-ba24-4e32-bdf6-7119f5bd08f2/status?status=CREATED
